name: Fiber
description: Tangled treasures from island grass.

name: Wood
description: Sun-kissed timber harvested from majestic palm trees. Ideal for crafting and roasting marshmallows (if you can find any).

name: Seaweed Fiber
description: Seashore secret for crafting needs.

name: Seashell Calcium
description: Calcium-rich treasures from seashells.

name: Fish Scales
description: Gleaming scales from the planet’s fishes.

name: Coralium
description: Vibrant oceanic resource harvested from corals.

name: Abyssallite
description: Deep-sea gem, hidden in the depths. A rare find for adventurous divers.

name: Kelp Iron
description: Iron with a touch of kelp magic.

name: Sea Urchin Spines
description: Prickly prizes from deep-sea urchins.

name: Leviathan Skin
description: A testament to conquering the sea's mightiest.

name: Leviathan Tooth
description: Enormous tooth of the legendary Leviathan. Handle carefully, display proudly.

name: Crystalline Tear
description: Glistening tear shed by the Blackened Eye.

name: Deep Tentacle
description: Sinister tentacle harvested from the dreaded Devourer.

name: Luminitite
description: Glowing mineral illuminating the caves.

name: Doomstone
description: Foreboding stone found in the depths of the island's caves.

name: Dreadworm Eye
description: Eerie eye, snatched from the fearsome Dreadworm. Peer into its unsettling gaze.

name: Alien Artifact
description: From the depths of the cave comes this mysterious artifact. Is it a remnant of an ancient civilization or something else?

name: Tritonite
description: A rare and precious gemstone found by vanquishing the formidable Krakolith. This gem holds the power to unlock new realms of knowledge. Keep it safe and wear it proudly as a badge of honor!

name: Seashell Plate
description: Finally, a use for all those seashells you've been collecting on the beach!

name: Sea Glass
description: The shimmering beauty of this glass is unmatched. It captures the colors of the ocean and adds a touch of elegance to any setting.

name: Silicon
description: A vital component in many technological advancements, Silicon is an essential material for any inventor or craftsman.

name: Abyssal Crystal
description: For when you need a crystal that's as dark and mysterious as your soul. It has magical properties that can enhance a variety of items.

name: Mermaid Metal
description: This sturdy metal is both beautiful and functional. Its unique composition makes it resistant to rust and corrosion, making it ideal for use in marine environments.

name: Coral Steel
description: A type of steel that has been reinforced with coral fragments, giving it extra strength and durability.

name: Calcified Abyssallite
description: Why settle for regular old metal when you can have something that sounds like a fancy medical condition?

name: Twilight Glow
description: This mysterious material emits a soft, ethereal glow. Its uses are not yet fully understood, but its potential is limitless.

name: Soil
description: A pile of dirt. It's not much, but it's all you've got.

name: Cloth
description: Who knew that a bunch of fibers could be turned into something so soft and comfortable?

name: Wood Plank
description: A staple of shipbuilding. They're strong and lightweight, making them ideal for a variety of construction projects.

name: Laser Gun Plasma
description: This high-tech material is a key component in laser weaponry. Its properties allow for highly concentrated and precise beams of energy.

name: Circuit Board
description: The puzzle that makes your computer go beep boop.

name: Hook
description: Great for pulling yourself back from the edge of insanity.

name: Metal Rod
description: A stick, but fancier.

name: Deep Sea Infused Plate
description: A thick, sturdy plate made of metal or composite material, used to protect the body from harm in combat or other dangerous situations.

name: Torpedo
description: For use only with the Torpedo Launcher.

name: Orange
description: Prickly fruits for a poke-filled harvest. Watch out for juicy surprises!

name: Quarkberries
description: Sweet and peculiar, just like this place.

name: Sea Meat
description: Savory bounty from the ocean's creatures.

name: Orange Jam
description: For when you want a meal that's both juicy and slimy. Yum!

name: Fish Stew
description: For when you want a meal that's both prickly and slimy. Yum!

name: Questionable Seafood
description: This dish may make you question your life choices, but at least you'll have a full belly. Just make sure you have plenty of water on hand, because it's guaranteed to make you thirsty. And maybe keep a bucket nearby, just in case.

name: Leviathan Schnitzel
description: It's time for payback! Feast on the crispy Leviathan skin and feel the thrill of victory over the once-mighty sea creature.

name: Crunchy Delight
description: It's so delicious, it'll bring tears to your eyes. Whether it's tears of joy or tears of pain is up to you.

name: Ointment
description: This ointment is a must-have for any researcher. Its healing properties make it ideal for treating cuts, scrapes, and other injuries. Wait, you're not eating it are you?

name: Cooking Pot
description: A device that can cook a variety of ingredients into a hearty stew, with the help of a built-in mixer and heating elements.

name: Fabricator
description: A multi-purpose machine that can be used to craft a wide range of items from various materials. It uses a combination of robotic arms, lasers, and 3D printing technology.

name: Smelter
description: A high-temperature furnace that can melt down minerals and metals into more useful forms. It's capable of producing alloys and other complex materials.

name: Assembler
description: A device that can be used to construct complex objects from smaller parts. It uses precise robotic arms and advanced algorithms to put everything together.

name: Fish Net
description: Finally, a way to catch fish without all that tedious fishing. Just toss it overboard and let it do the work for you.

name: Sticky Glow Pods
description: These pods stick to just about anything and emit a soft, comforting glow. They're perfect for lighting up dark corners of caves.

name: Boat
description: Because sometimes you just need to sail away from all your problems.

name: Anchor Line
description: Allows you to quickly ascend to your boat. Needs a direct line of sight.

name: Sonar
description: Tired of being ambushed by angry sea creatures? Fear not! This sonar lets you detect enemies before they detect you, and locate valuable resources to boot.

name: Reaper’s Call
description: The dread summons, a beckoning from beyond. Pray to your gods, for when it answers, all shall be consumed by the abyss.

name: Flippers
description: When you want to swim like a fish, but still keep your human dignity.

name: Oxygen Tank
description: This essential piece of diving equipment lets you stay submerged and explore for extended periods without worrying about running out of breath.

name: Abyssal Tank
description: This tank will keep you alive in the darkest depths of the ocean, but at what cost? Who knows what horrors lurk down there…

name: Suction Drill
description: Finally, a drill that sucks in a good way! Perfect for those who want to dig deep and collect precious materials without breaking a sweat.

name: Spear
description: The perfect tool for when you want to stab something, but don't want to get too close.

name: Laser Gun
description: An advanced and versatile weapon that uses laser technology to deliver devastating energy beams. Handle with caution.

name: Trident
description: The perfect weapon for your underwater adventures or your 'Little Mermaid' cosplay, whichever comes first.

name: Torpedo Launcher
description: Want to send a message to that pesky Leviathan that's been harassing you? Look no further than the Torpedo Launcher!
